Eko Hotels And Suites played host to the sixth edition of the Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards on the 1st of September with its hosts, Joselyn Dumas and Bovi. The event also saw 120 nominations from Ghana, Kenya, Malawi, Nigeria and South Africa battle in 27 categories. Here is the complete list of the winners: Best Sound Editor
